</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Select "Cookies and site permissions" 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-018E33A1-C8B0-4A57-B3EB-B02EB3CA697A" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title ">Cookies and site permissions</title><image href="GUID-809202A1-974A-4DE7-8BB4-C446031AF66D-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-809202A1-974A-4DE7-8BB4-C446031AF66D-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Click on PDF documents. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-F2CBFA2D-9F67-48BB-AEAA-4F2E79AF064F" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title ">PDF documents</title><image href="GUID-C62F10AC-76A5-4616-A2CD-ADE195819944-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-C62F10AC-76A5-4616-A2CD-ADE195819944-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Enable the indicated option "Always download PDF files".
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-A1AE0B25-69F5-4C94-A302-402BA7936DCD" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title ">Option Always download PDF files</title><image href="GUID-87A071E7-F130-4F99-ADD9-10D0F204E34F-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-87A071E7-F130-4F99-ADD9-10D0F204E34F-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5
